data.description: **MOTIVATED SELLER**PRICED TO SELL**Offering Buyer a $10,000 Custom Closet Bonus AND a Supreme 2-10 Home Warranty!  Come see you or your client's future dream home in the heart of Alpharetta!  This stunning, brand new two story contemporary craftsman is walking distance to everything Alpharetta, but still comes with all the quiet charm that Alpharetta has to offer.  This home is perfectly situated on an over half acre lot, with a 2 car garage, private backyard and an incredible outdoor kitchen, complete with refrigeration, an Al Fresco Grill, hot and cold sink, the works!  The interior kitchen comes with a complete Thermador stainless steel appliance package, including a 48" range, speed oven, built-in oversize refrigerator, dual zone wine cooler, and dishwasher.  The large kitchen island and open floor plan on the main level is breathtaking!  There are beautiful hardwoods throughout, while all bedrooms and bathrooms come with stylish, luxury carpeting and tile respectively.  The master bedroom features vaulted ceilings, exposed beams, and a private sitting room.  The master bathroom features a large walk-in glass shower and a separate stand alone bathtub.  The private, upstairs office overlooks the front yard.  Lastly, the other bedrooms and bathrooms are very spacious, coupled with tons of natural light!  Come make you or your client's home buying dreams a reality!
